    <para id="id13289965">For a doping level of N<sub>D</sub> = 10<sup>20</sup>/cc, ∆E<sub>g</sub>=0.12eV.</para>
    <para id="id13142214">This gives an effective doping level of N<sub>Deff</sub> = 10<sup>18</sup>/cc.</para>
    <para id="id12976858">The classical formula for current gain without BGN is:</para>
    <para id="id14277265">
      <figure id="id8161966">
        <media id="id8161966_media" alt="">
