    </para>
    <para id="id10016796">If we take the following data: (N<sub>D</sub>)<sub>E</sub> = 10<sup>20</sup>/cc, (N<sub>A</sub>)<sub>B</sub> = 10<sup>17</sup>/cc, W<sub>E</sub> = W<sub>B</sub> = 1µm and D<sub>pE</sub>=1.25 (cm)<sup>2</sup>/sec and D<sub>nB</sub>=20 (cm)<sup>2</sup>/sec then β<sub>F</sub> = 1.6×10<sup>4</sup> ;</para>
    <para id="id14206026">But taking into account of BGN, β<sub>F</sub> = 160.</para>
